Class Contractor

java.lang.Object
  suncertify.model.Contractor
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Contractor>
Direct Known Subclasses:
ContractorCriteria
public class Contractor
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Contractor>

Encapsulates single contractor entity information to be persisted or currently resides in a persistence storage.

This class supports properties changes notification by using PropertyChangeListener.Property names are:

  • name
  • location
  • specialties
  • size
  • rate
  • owner

Author:
Mohammad S. Abdellatif
